## Superseded: ci-cd-remove-upstream-fixed-workaround-fan-out-matrix

```yaml
name: ci-cd-remove-upstream-fixed-workaround-fan-out-matrix
description: "Pattern for safely removing a CI matrix workaround once an upstream bug is fixed: convert sequential single-runner steps back to a multi-entry matrix. Each just test-group invocation must remain its OWN step gated by if: matrix.group == 'X' so coverage-validation parsers keep working."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-05-10
version: "1.0.0"
user-invocable: false
verification: verified-precommit
```

Verified on ProjectOdyssey PR #5381 (removing modular/modular#6433 workaround).

