name: ci-github-ruleset-matrix-status-context
description: "GitHub matrix jobs emit expanded context names (job-id (matrix-value)) that must be registered verbatim in branch rulesets. Use when: (1) a required status check shows 'Expected — Waiting for status to be reported' forever, (2) a ruleset uses the bare job ID for a matrix job, (3) debugging why classic branch protection returns 404 but the PR is still blocked."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-04-26
version: "1.0.0"
user-invocable: false
verification: verified-local
```

Verified on ProjectKeystone PR #451 (ruleset ID 15556488, four sanitizer matrix values).

