## Superseded: judge-rerun-workspace-corruption

```yaml
name: judge-rerun-workspace-corruption
description: Fix judge reruns producing incorrect results due to workspace corruption
category: architecture
date: 2026-02-09
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Save judge_prompt.md at execution time; reuse on reruns; block workspace recreation for completed
runs; remove fallback judges that mask failures. Eliminated 2307/3600 garbage judgments.

